    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain your <strong>king prawns</strong></p><p>Once thickened, stir in your <strong>salmon flakes</strong>, <strong>drained king prawns</strong>, <strong>blanched peas </strong>and <strong>chopped dill</strong></p><p>Cook for 1-2 min further until fully combined – this is your <strong>fish pie mix</strong></p><p>Transfer the <strong>fish pie mix </strong>to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1611674374803-x200.jpg",
