        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Mash the <strong>drained potatoes</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Tip: Don't worry if you're left with a crumbly mixture, this helps add texture to your topping!</p><p>Top the fish pie mix evenly with the <strong>mashed potatoes</strong> and put the dish in the oven for 20-25 min or until the prawns are cooked through and the topping is lightly golden – this is your <strong>salmon & king prawn fish pie</strong></p>",
