      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the fish pie cooks, add the <strong>chopped chives</strong>, <strong>remaining chopped garlic</strong> and 1.5 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 1/2 tbsp]<strong> </span>butter</strong> to a bowl</p><p>Use a fork to mix everything together evenly by pressing the mixture against the bowl – this is your <strong>herby</strong> <strong>garlic butter</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lemon</strong> into wedges</p>",
