    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the fish pie has been cooking for 15 min, reboil half a kettle</p><p>Trim, then add your<strong> green beans</strong> to a pot (use the mash pot to save on washing up!)</p><p>Cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 3-4 min or until tender</p><p>Once done, drain the beans, return them to the pot and keep covered until serving</p>",
