    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once cooked, remove the <strong>salmon & king prawn fish pie </strong>from the oven and spoon the <strong>herby garlic butter</strong> all over the top, then leave to stand for 5 min before serving</p><p>Tip: Cooling it slightly helps the sauce to thicken up and will let the herby garlic butter melt all over!</p><p>Serve the <strong>salmon & king prawn fish pie</strong> with the <strong>green beans</strong> and a <strong>lemon wedge</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
